{
  "id": "63ca0af347bc70001dab9e26",
  "title": "線を引くUI",
  "created": 1674185462,
  "updated": 1674714147,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "63ca0af347bc70001dab9e26",
      "text": "線を引くUI",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674185462,
      "updated": 1674185465
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca0b58aff09e0000e8f989",
      "text": "二つの要素の間に線を引き、要素が移動されてもつながり続けて欲しい、というユースケースをどうやって実現するか",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674185561,
      "updated": 1674185577
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca0b59aff09e0000e8f98a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674185562,
      "updated": 1674185562
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca0afaaff09e000092c98d",
      "text": "Kozanebaの線を引くUIを改善しようと考えている[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674185467,
      "updated": 1674185563
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca0b12aff09e000092c98f",
      "text": "\t一旦内部の設計の都合は置いといて「線を引くUI」にはどのようなものがあるか考える",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674185491,
      "updated": 1674185564
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca0b53aff09e0000e8f973",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674185556,
      "updated": 1674185556
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca0b53aff09e0000e8f974",
      "text": "実装方法1:",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674185556,
      "updated": 1674185556
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca0b53aff09e0000e8f975",
      "text": " 線を引くモードを導入する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674185556,
      "updated": 1674185556
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca0b53aff09e0000e8f976",
      "text": " 要素Aと要素Bをクリックすると線が引かれる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674185556,
      "updated": 1674185556
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca0b53aff09e0000e8f977",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674185556,
      "updated": 1674185556
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca0b53aff09e0000e8f978",
      "text": "実装方法2:",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674185556,
      "updated": 1674185556
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca0b53aff09e0000e8f979",
      "text": " 線を引くモードを導入する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674185556,
      "updated": 1674185556
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca0b53aff09e0000e8f97a",
      "text": " 要素Aでポインターダウン、要素Bでポインターアップすると線が引かれる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674185556,
      "updated": 1674185556
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca0b53aff09e0000e8f97b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674185556,
      "updated": 1674185556
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca0b53aff09e0000e8f97c",
      "text": "実装方法3:",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674185556,
      "updated": 1674185556
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca0b53aff09e0000e8f97d",
      "text": " 複数の要素を選択する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674185556,
      "updated": 1674185556
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca0b53aff09e0000e8f97e",
      "text": "　 コンテキストメニューが現れる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674185556,
      "updated": 1674185556
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca0b53aff09e0000e8f97f",
      "text": " メニューから「線を引く」を選ぶ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674185556,
      "updated": 1674185556
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca0b53aff09e0000e8f980",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674185556,
      "updated": 1674185556
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca0b53aff09e0000e8f981",
      "text": "実装方法4:",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674185556,
      "updated": 1674185556
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca0b53aff09e0000e8f982",
      "text": " グローバルのメニューで「線を追加」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674185556,
      "updated": 1674185556
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca0b53aff09e0000e8f983",
      "text": "　両端がnullの線ができる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674185556,
      "updated": 1674185556
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca0b53aff09e0000e8f984",
      "text": "　それを要素A、要素Bにドラッグドロップすると接続される",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674185556,
      "updated": 1674185556
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca0b53aff09e0000e8f985",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674185556,
      "updated": 1674185556
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca0b53aff09e0000e8f986",
      "text": "実装方法5:",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674185556,
      "updated": 1674185556
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca0b53aff09e0000e8f987",
      "text": " 要素Aのクリックでハンドルが現れる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674185556,
      "updated": 1674185556
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca0b53aff09e0000e8f988",
      "text": " ハンドルを要素Bにドラッグドロップすると線が引かれる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674185556,
      "updated": 1674185556
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca0bdcaff09e000092c990",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674185693,
      "updated": 1674185693
    },
    {
      "id": "63d21c1eaff09e000047b381",
      "text": "[** 考察]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674714142,
      "updated": 1674714147
    },
    {
      "id": "63d21c1eaff09e000047b382",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674714142,
      "updated": 1674714142
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca0bddaff09e000092c991",
      "text": "線を引くモードについて",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674185693,
      "updated": 1674185701
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca0be0aff09e000092c993",
      "text": "　まとめて線を引くならモードに入るのが楽",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674185696,
      "updated": 1674185718
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca0bf6aff09e000092c994",
      "text": "　線を引いて要素を動かして、が頻繁に切り替わるならその度にモード切り替えが必要になって手間",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674185718,
      "updated": 1674185747
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca0c13aff09e000092c995",
      "text": "　　「いま自分がどのモードか」を把握する必要がある",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674185747,
      "updated": 1674185786
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca0c3aaff09e000092c996",
      "text": "　　要素を動かそうとして線を引いてしまう人が出る",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674185786,
      "updated": 1674185786
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca0ec4aff09e000092c9ab",
      "text": "　Google Slideは実装方法2",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674186436,
      "updated": 1674186454
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca0ed5aff09e000092c9ac",
      "text": "  ドラッグドロップの対象は要素自身ではなくハンドル",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674186454,
      "updated": 1674186475
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca0be0aff09e000092c992",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674185696,
      "updated": 1674185696
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca0c42aff09e000092c997",
      "text": "実装方法3",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674185794,
      "updated": 1674185807
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca0c4faff09e000092c999",
      "text": " 現状のKozanebaの実装",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674185807,
      "updated": 1674185817
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca0c6eaff09e000092c99b",
      "text": " 二要素間の関係に限らず表現できることがメリット",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674185838,
      "updated": 1674185866
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca0c61aff09e000092c99a",
      "text": " 近いものに線を引くなら許容できる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674185826,
      "updated": 1674185906
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca0cb1aff09e000092c99d",
      "text": " 遠くのものに線を引こうとした時や入り組んだ配置の時に「範囲選択」で他のものを巻き込んでしまう",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674185906,
      "updated": 1674185948
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca0cdcaff09e000092c99e",
      "text": " 　運用による回避手段",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674185949,
      "updated": 1674185960
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca0ce8aff09e000092c99f",
      "text": " 　　対象要素を近くに移動する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674185960,
      "updated": 1674185974
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca0cf6aff09e000092c9a0",
      "text": " 　　線を引く",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674185974,
      "updated": 1674185978
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca0cfaaff09e000092c9a1",
      "text": " 　　元の場所に戻す",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674185978,
      "updated": 1674185983
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca0cffaff09e000092c9a2",
      "text": " 　これは面倒！",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674185984,
      "updated": 1674185988
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca0d04aff09e000092c9a3",
      "text": " 　線の機能を作って使ってみているうちに、思っていた以上にこういう状況が多発して面倒だと気づいた",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674185988,
      "updated": 1674186034
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca0d32aff09e000092c9a4",
      "text": " 　　多項関係を掛けるメリットを上回るデメリットだと思うようになった",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674186035,
      "updated": 1674186062
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca0d4eaff09e000092c9a5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674186063,
      "updated": 1674186063
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca0d4faff09e000092c9a6",
      "text": "実装方法4",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674186063,
      "updated": 1674186074
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca0d5aaff09e000092c9a7",
      "text": " Keynoteは線のボタンを押した時点で線が追加される",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674186074,
      "updated": 1674186297
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca0e3aaff09e000092c9a8",
      "text": " 　要素に接続はしない？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674186298,
      "updated": 1674186311
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca151baff09e0000af84d2",
      "text": " Google Slideも「線を引くモード」でクリックをするとこれになる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674188060,
      "updated": 1674188085
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca0e42aff09e000092c9a9",
      "text": " 一時的に「どこにもつながっていない線」ができるので「線とは要素を繋ぐものである」と定義していると問題が起きる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674186307,
      "updated": 1674186361
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca0e7caff09e000092c9aa",
      "text": " 　設計時に注意が必要",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674186365,
      "updated": 1674186373
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca0c4eaff09e000092c998",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674185806,
      "updated": 1674185806
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca0f01aff09e000092c9ad",
      "text": "実装方法5",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674186498,
      "updated": 1674186501
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca0f15aff09e000092c9b1",
      "text": "　Miroの実装",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674186518,
      "updated": 1674186526
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca0f23aff09e000092c9b2",
      "text": "　　現状のKozanebaも要素をクリックするとコンテキストメニューが出るので「一時的なモードに入っている」という点では同じ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674186531,
      "updated": 1674186563
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca0f06aff09e000092c9b0",
      "text": " 　　ハンドルを出すことはできる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674186503,
      "updated": 1674186618
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca0f7baff09e000092c9b3",
      "text": "　　　ハンドルでポインターダウンした時点で「一時的なメニューを出すモード」が「一時的な線を引くモード」に切り替わる必要がある",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674186620,
      "updated": 1674187065
    },
    {
      "id": "63ca0f04aff09e000092c9ae",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1674186500,
      "updated": 1674186500
    }
  ]
}